<h1>Calculate Finance Charges</h1>

<p class=Body-Text>Use this function to automatically calculate finance 
 charges on all outstanding balances.</p>

<ol>
	
	<li class=kadov-p-CList-Number><p class=List-Number>From the main menu, 
 select <span style="font-weight: bold;"><B>Accounting, Calculate Finance 
 Charges</B></span>. &nbsp;The 
 <a class=dropspot
	x-use-popup=#POPUP215262495
	x-popup-type=pulldown
	href="javascript:kadovTextPopup(this)"
	id=a1>Finance Charge Calculations window</a> 
 displays.</p>
<div class="droptext" id="POPUP215262495" style="display: 'none'; " x-ss-type="dropdown">
 <p class="whs1"><img src="calculate_finance_Charges.gif" x-maintain-ratio="TRUE" width="730px" height="192px" border="0" class="img_whs2"></p>
</div></li>
	
	<li class=kadov-p-CList-Number><p class=List-Number><span style="font-weight: bold;"><B>Date 
 Finance Charges Last Run.</B></span> &nbsp;Enter 
 the date on which finances charges were last run. &nbsp;<span 
 style="color: #ff0000; font-weight: bold;"><font color=red ><B>IMPORTANT:</B></font></span> 
 You must &nbsp;enter 
 an accurate date in this field to ensure that finance charges aren't duplicated.</p></li>
	
	<li class=kadov-p-CList-Number><p class=List-Number><span style="font-weight: bold;"><B>Calculate 
 Finance Charges Through.</B></span> &nbsp;Enter 
 the date through which finance charges should be calculated.</p></li>
	
	<li class=kadov-p-CList-Number><p class=List-Number>When both entries 
 are made, click the <span style="font-weight: bold;"><B>Calculate </B></span>button. 
 &nbsp;The <a 
 class=dropspot
	x-use-popup=#POPUP214585974
	x-popup-type=pulldown
	href="javascript:kadovTextPopup(this)"
	id=a2>Finance Charge Preview window</a> 
 displays.</p>
<div class="droptext" id="POPUP214585974" style="display: 'none'; " x-ss-type="dropdown">
 <p class="whs1"><img src="finance_charge_preview.gif" x-maintain-ratio="TRUE" width="730px" height="194px" border="0" class="img_whs3"></p>
</div></li>
	
	<li class=kadov-p-CList-Number><p class=List-Number>Review the preview 
 information. &nbsp;All 
 items with a checkmark are deemed &quot;selected&quot; and the finance 
 charge will be applied to the account. &nbsp;To 
 unselect any 
 item, click in the checkbox under the <span style="font-style: italic;"><I>Selected 
 </I></span><span>heading to remove the checkmark.</span></p></li>
	
	<li class=kadov-p-CList-Number><p class=List-Number>When you have selected 
 the desired line items, and verified the data, click the <span style="font-weight: bold;"><B>Save 
 </B></span>button. &nbsp;The 
 data is saved and you return to the Accounting window.</p></li>
</ol>

